Dear {{NAME}},

We are pleased to inform you that your paper #{{PID}}, titled "{{TITLE}}", has been conditionally accepted for inclusion in the {{CONFNAME}} conference technical program.

Please note that your paper requires revisions before final acceptance. The detailed revision instructions are provided in the "Add comment" section in {{LINK}}. You are required to carefully address each comment listed there and submit both:

1. The revised manuscript, with all changes clearly highlighted; and

2. A point-by-point response document explaining how all reviewer comments have been addressed.

Both the revised manuscript and the response document should be submitted via the "Add comment" section in {{LINK}}.

The deadline for submitting the revised version and response is October 22, 2025. After review of your revised submission, the paper will be formally accepted once the TPC Chairs confirm that all comments have been satisfactorily addressed.

If your paper is officially accepted, please complete your registration before the registration deadline on October 31, 2025.

We appreciate your contribution and look forward to your revised submission and to seeing you at {{CONFNAME}}.

* Title: {{TITLE}}
* Author(s): {{OPT(AUTHORS)}}
* Site: {{LINK(paper, p={{PID}}, {{AUTHORVIEWCAPABILITY}})}}

