Thank you for submitting your paper #{{PID}}, titled "{{TITLE}}", to {{CONFNAME}}.

We regret to inform you that your paper has not been accepted for inclusion in the {{CONFNAME}} technical program. Due to the highly competitive review process and limited program space, many good submissions unfortunately could not be accommodated this year.

The review comments for your paper are available in {{LINK}}. We hope you find the feedback helpful for improving your work.

Although your paper could not be accepted, we warmly invite you to attend {{CONFNAME}}, which will be held in Hefei, China, from December 14-18, 2025. The conference will be held in person, offering valuable opportunities for networking and academic exchange.

We sincerely thank you for your submission and hope you will consider submitting your future work to ICPADS. We look forward to seeing you at {{CONFNAME}}.

